# Railway should only deploy the Python backend via Dockerfile.
# .dockerignore is the primary excluder; this file is a fallback in case
# Railway falls back to Nixpacks. Keep the two in sync.
#
# The root package.json + package-lock.json exist for local dev orchestration
# (`npm run dev`). They MUST NOT enter the Railway build context, or Nixpacks
# will detect Node and try to run `vite build` (it fails with vite: not found).

